      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This car is in truly exceptional condition and looks like it just left the showroom floor! It has been kept in pristine shape, with a flawless exterior and an interior that still feels brand new. You won't find a scratch or a blemish on this beauty\u2014it's a rare find for anyone looking for perfection in their next ride!",
